{"tid":1916530,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Jared Leto攀岩失事險喪命","createTime":"2020-03-09T02:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T05:56:41.000Z","uid":64191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b5df741b622aa8dbd4478a4ea78bceada2e937","tid":1916530,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"漫威《魔比斯》攀岩出意外！謝拉力圖差點命喪紅岩峽谷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吉人天相。曾在《自殺特攻：超能暴隊》中飾演「小丑」的謝拉力圖，日前去攀岩石，突發吊掛繩索被岩石割裂，導致他差點摔落粉身碎骨的意外！幸好靠著另一條配安全繩索的保護與隊友的幫忙，有驚無險，撿回一命。<br />\n<br />\n謝拉力圖在個人社群和網友分享驚險的親身經歷：他日前去拉斯維加斯附近知名的紅岩峽谷攀岩，享受挑戰體能的刺激感，與身處高空中飽覽美景的滿足感。<br />\n<br />\n不料繫在身上的一條繩索被岩石割裂，讓他疾速往下墜落近600英尺（約182.88公尺），謝拉力圖形容：「一點都不誇張，當時我真真正正感覺自己快要沒命了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hXLXMzY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhXLXMzY.jpg&h=c5be712d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲謝拉力圖在個人社群和網友分享攀岩的親身「驚」歷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幸好他身上還有配備另一條安全防護繩索，而且他並非單獨行動，在隊友艾力克斯洪諾的全力搶救下，才緊急拉住謝拉力圖，並慢慢拉他上來到安全地方，撿回一命。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友恭喜他福大命大，生死交戰，劫後餘生；但謝拉力圖自爆親生「驚」歷的用心，是希望和他同樣喜歡攀岩的人士，一定要注意配備等各種安全措施，而且最好要有隊友相伴，必要時互相幫助。<br />\n<br />\n今年48歲的謝拉力圖，曾以《續命梟雄》贏得2014年奧斯卡最佳男配角；曾在2016年DC漫畫改編的《自殺特攻：超能暴隊》中飾演「小丑」，當時他的驚悚造型與表演方式，曾造成轟動的話題。<br />\n<br />\n而接下來他更有驚人之作，在「漫威」原創漫畫改編的《魔比斯》中，飾演原本是罕見血液科學家的「魔比斯」卻在治療過程中變成吸血鬼&hellip;是謝拉力圖首度演出「漫威」的電影，台灣預定今年7月31日公映。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/j7da2M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2Fj7da2M&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=fba48504\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/j7da2M</a>"},{"pid":"12856c55cbebf5b0a8a2354fa80cda2886ab8e71","tid":1916530,"uid":217641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"讓他疾速往下墜落近600英尺（約182.88公尺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4167abcb7f31102d28ddd3263753318ef32dbe0","tid":1916530,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"如果free solo就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96699151a9afb242c8adf923e3c978db3fed694","tid":1916530,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:50:29.000Z","msg":"就黎死都仲IG打卡?"},{"pid":"300b4ad0b9cb492f5b18b95f701b859814aacfb2","tid":1916530,"uid":79993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:53:35.000Z","msg":"曾在2016年DC漫畫改編的《自殺特攻：超能暴隊》中飾演「小丑」，<span style=\"color: red;\">當時他的驚悚造型與表演方式，曾造成轟動的話題。</span><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a51292694862bbc6dfc7c68c911f35ac8a2710","tid":1916530,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12856c55cbebf5b0a8a2354fa80cda2886ab8e71","tid":1916530,"uid":217641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"讓他疾速往下墜落近600英尺（約182.88公尺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"free fall 百幾米，我應該嚇到心都停埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e357a47a57ac4fea90e5eb8b928eaa550dcf922a","tid":1916530,"uid":36167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:45:01.000Z","msg":"Dangled some 600 ft in the air係下墜六百英尺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62eeaf643c100a9f7fcc3bfcf50b32cc4dcf6b1","tid":1916530,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/910313cb7ab0713e5d50bab573a7f5c7/tumblr_obwohfxou01vs6xh0o1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F910313cb7ab0713e5d50bab573a7f5c7%2Ftumblr_obwohfxou01vs6xh0o1_500.gif&h=4c91aca7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}